      "credits or membership are cash, income, reimbursement, voting control, live trading permission, leverage, custody, withdrawals, or risk-control bypass",
      "the 10,000 GCA member benefit is automatic or self-service transferred before holding-period verification, support approval, and manual reserve-wallet processing",
      "the 10,000 GCA member benefit is newly minted, guaranteed income, reimbursement, or trading permission",
